Update Notice


15 Jun 2015 06:48






Noting here that I've updated on the SCP. To be specific, I've changed Addendum 2144-1 into something more subtle and does not cry out  directly (since I suspect everyone would have figured it out on their own. If not, my Authorial posts have spoiled it.).

Furthermore, I do think that the dream diaries might have been a bit too . The content of the dream diaries still stands, although they are never recorded and only Schmidt and Mel know about it.

I have brought back the collar from the original article, although it is just a normal collar now.

EDIT: And I have also shamelessly put in one of my author avatars into this SCP to introduce her in the meta-narrative of Foundation-verse. It makes sense in-context, since An's job is a containment advisor.





